OL,3,CNational Slate Museum secures #12
OL,4,Cmillion in funding
OL,6,FAmgueddfa Cymru has secured #12
OL,7,Fmillion for the redevelopment of the
OL,8,FNational Slate Museum in Llanberis.
OL,10,FThe money was awarded by The National
OL,11,FLottery Heritage Fund and will help
OL,12,Fprotect the future of the museum.
OL,14,FThe Grade 1 listed building has been
OL,15,Fhome to the National Slate Museum
OL,16,Fsince 1972, when it was first opened
OL,17,Fto the public after the closure of
OL,18,FDinorwig slate quarry in 1969.
