OL,3,CNational Slate Museum secures #12
OL,4,Cmillion in funding
OL,6,FNow, the money will go to create a new
OL,7,Flearning centre, play area, shop and
OL,8,Fcafe, as well as improving
OL,9,Faccessibility throughout the site.
OL,11,FAmgueddfa Cymru said that Welsh
OL,12,Flanguage will be embedded at all
OL,13,Fstages of the project to celebrate how
OL,14,Fthe slate industry helped the language
OL,15,Fthrive in the area.
