OL,3,CNational Slate Museum secures #12
OL,4,Cmillion in funding
OL,6,FThe Chief Executive of the museum,
OL,7,FJane Richardson said: "We are truly
OL,8,Fthrilled to have been awarded this
OL,9,Fsignificant grant from The National
OL,10,FLottery Heritage Fund which means we
OL,11,Fcan progress the redevelopment plans
OL,12,Fwith certainty.
OL,14,F"This is a key milestone in the
OL,15,FLlanberis redevelopment project and is
OL,16,Fexciting news for us, for the wider
OL,17,Fcommunity, and for everyone in Wales.
