OL,6,F"Thanks to National Lottery players,
OL,7,Fwe can now conserve the history of the
OL,8,FNational Slate Museum for future
OL,9,Fgenerations and move towards a more
OL,10,Fsustainable future for the Museum
OL,11,Fwhich will be more inclusive, more
OL,12,Faccessible, and which will inspire
OL,13,Fgrowth and learning.
OL,15,F"This will mean even more people can
OL,16,Faccess and enjoy the global success
OL,17,Fstory of NorthJWales slate."
